column5: Oh man! Amazing outing. Love your setup too.
Peace and quiet.....how can you not like that. Beautiful specks as well. Thanks for sharing.
Love the back woods reports , thanks .

Thanks for the comments gang! Yes indeed, they are naturals. This is the main reason why I only fish this lake once or twice a year. I really don't want to put too much pressure on such a small but magical lake. I've respectfully fished it with great success for the last 20 years and hopefully for the next 20 as well.
Great fishin' bud.  Always enjoy your speckie from the toob reports.  Some wicked colors on that bunch "up there."
